dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2527895\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2527895\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 03, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104gkm1665702892640.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/gkm1665702892640.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/gkm1665702892640.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"gkm1665702892640\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Uniface as a DDE Client\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"gkm1665702892640__uniface_as_a_dde_client_113983\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gkm1665702892640__p_d35546e1_d35547e1_d35548e1\">Uniface provides the following operations to request, send, and execute DDE transactions using the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">activate</span> ProcScript statement:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gkm1665702892640__li_d18236e1_d18237e1_d18238e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">uDdeRequest</span>—gets data from the server application\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gkm1665702892640__li_d18239e1_d18240e1_d18241e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">uDdePoke</span>—sends updated data to the server application (puts data in the application)\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gkm1665702892640__li_d18242e1_d18243e1_d18244e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">uDdeExecute</span>—sends commands in the server application\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gkm1665702892640__li_d18245e1_d18246e1_d18247e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">uDdeAdvise</span>—establishes an automatic link (warm link)\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gkm1665702892640__li_d18248e1_d18249e1_d18250e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">uDdeUnadvise</span>—cancels a warm link\n </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gkm1665702892640__p_d35549e1_d35550e1_d35551e1\">The procedures <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">uDdeRequest</span>, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">uDdeAdvise</span>, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">uDdePoke</span>, and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">uDdeExecute</span> normally have a time-out of one second. They will return failure (<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span> is <code class=\"ph codeph\">-1</code>) if the DDE transaction is not completed within that time.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gkm1665702892640__p_d35552e1_d35553e1_d35554e1\">For some applications, this time-out is too short. To adjust the time-out value, set the value of the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">TimeOut</span> setting in the [udde] section of the <span class=\"ph filepath\">.ini</span> file.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gkm1665702892640__topic_d23212e1_d23213e1_d23214e1_d23215e1_d23216e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1038337e127\">\n                  \n Scripting UDDE Client Requests\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gkm1665702892640__p_d35558e1_d35559e1_d35560e1\">Setting up a Uniface application as a DDE client requires some ProcScript programming because Uniface does not offer a <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Paste Link</span> command.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gkm1665702892640__p_d35561e1_d35562e1_d35563e1\">All DDE transactions require the client to specify an address containing the following strings:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gkm1665702892640__li_d18251e1_d18252e1_d18253e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Service</var>—identifies the DDE server application\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gkm1665702892640__li_d18254e1_d18255e1_d18256e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Topic</var>—often identifies a document, a worksheet, or a Uniface component\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gkm1665702892640__li_d18257e1_d18258e1_d18259e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Item</var>—identifies exactly which part of the topic is requested, for example, a cell in a spreadsheet, a bookmark in a word processing application, or a field in Uniface.\n </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gkm1665702892640__p_d35564e1_d35565e1_d35566e1\">The operations provided by UDDE do not support parameters, so you need to assign this information to general variables, such as $51, $52, and so on. For example:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$50=\"Calc\"\n$51=\"system\"\n$53=\"[Open(%%\"c:/wrksht.ods%%\")][Select(%%\"R4C5%%\")][Formula(%%\"%%field%%%%%\")]\"\nactivate \"udde\".uDdeExecute()\nif ($status=0)\n message \"Execute succeeded\"\nelse\n message \"Execute did not succeed\"\nendif\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fkg1719680200265.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>DDE Links</a><p>Applications that communiicate via DDE do so using links that can be defined by copying and pasting them to the destination application or programming them using the DDE syntax rules.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/clk1665702551274.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Variables</a><p>Variables are placeholders for data whose value can change during the runtime duration of the ProcScript module, component, or application for which they have scope. The scope is determined by where they are declared.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527895\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527895\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Uniface as a DDE Client Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 03, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Uniface as a DDE Client Uniface provides the following operations to request, send, and execute DDE transactions using the activate ProcScript statement: uDdeRequest —gets data from the server application uDdePoke —sends updated data to the server application (puts data in the application) uDdeExecute —sends commands in the server application uDdeAdvise —establishes an automatic link (warm link) uDdeUnadvise —cancels a warm link The procedures uDdeRequest , uDdeAdvise , uDdePoke , and uDdeExecute normally have a time-out of one second. They will return failure ( $status is -1 ) if the DDE transaction is not completed within that time. For some applications, this time-out is too short. To adjust the time-out value, set the value of the TimeOut setting in the [udde] section of the .ini file. Scripting UDDE Client Requests Setting up a Uniface application as a DDE client requires some ProcScript programming because Uniface does not offer a Paste Link command. All DDE transactions require the client to specify an address containing the following strings: Service —identifies the DDE server application Topic —often identifies a document, a worksheet, or a Uniface component Item —identifies exactly which part of the topic is requested, for example, a cell in a spreadsheet, a bookmark in a word processing application, or a field in Uniface. The operations provided by UDDE do not support parameters, so you need to assign this information to general variables, such as $51, $52, and so on. For example: $50=\"Calc\" $51=\"system\" $53=\"[Open(%%\"c:/wrksht.ods%%\")][Select(%%\"R4C5%%\")][Formula(%%\"%%field%%%%%\")]\" activate \"udde\".uDdeExecute() if ($status=0) message \"Execute succeeded\" else message \"Execute did not succeed\" endif Copy Related Links DDE Links Applications that communiicate via DDE do so using links that can be defined by copying and pasting them to the destination application or programming them using the DDE syntax rules. Variables Variables are placeholders for data whose value can change during the runtime duration of the ProcScript module, component, or application for which they have scope. The scope is determined by where they are declared. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}